*Veća* je voda u moru od vode u jezeru. (The water in the sea is larger than the water in the lake.)

*Veća* je zgrada od ostalih u ulici. (The building is larger than the others in the street.)

*Većom* brzinom ćete stići do cilja. (You will reach the destination faster with a greater speed.)

*Većeg* uspeha nema od ovog. (There is no greater success than this one.)

*Većih* izazova ne postoji. (There are no greater challenges.)